data.title: Deactivated NPI Numbers
data.meta_description: Deactivated NPI Numbers - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document contains information about healthcare providers including their NPI number, name, specialty, and date of deactivation. There are over 100 entries listing the provider's name, specialty such as dentist, counselor, or family practice physician, and date their provider status was deactivated. The specialties range widely from counseling and social work to various medical specialties including urology, optometry, and psychiatry.
